%% Status: NEEDS HUMAN REVIEW
sequenceDiagram
    participant EnrichmentPipeline
    participant SpeciesTable
    participant Client_AppStart
    participant LocalSpeciesTable
    participant ItemsProvider
    participant PackScreen

    EnrichmentPipeline->>SpeciesTable: UPDATE species row (art_url now non-null)

    Note over Client_AppStart: Client opens app or returns from background
    Client_AppStart->>SpeciesTable: SELECT id, common_name, icon_url, art_url, brawn, wit, speed, ...<br/>FROM species WHERE updated_at > :lastSyncTimestamp
    SpeciesTable-->>Client_AppStart: Changed species rows

    loop For each changed species
        Client_AppStart->>LocalSpeciesTable: UPSERT into LocalSpeciesTable
    end
    Client_AppStart->>Client_AppStart: Update lastSyncTimestamp

    ItemsProvider->>LocalSpeciesTable: Cross-reference items whose definition_id matches newly-enriched species
    LocalSpeciesTable-->>ItemsProvider: Matched items now have "fully enriched" predicate = true

    ItemsProvider->>PackScreen: Notify updated item state
    PackScreen->>PackScreen: Previously non-responsive cards now respond to hold gesture

    Note over PackScreen: No push notification.<br/>Player discovers organically.
